        "question": "Which Node.js and TypeScript versions do we need for Angular 19?",
        "answer": "Angular 19 officially supports Node 16 LTS and newer (Node 18 is recommended) and requires TypeScript 5.0 or later. The current project uses TypeScript 4.9.5, so both the `tsconfig.json` and the CI environment will need to be updated accordingly."
