        "question": "Will the vertical action bar still compile with Pattern Library 12.6.0?",
        "answer": "Yes, the vertical action bar is still shipped in PL 12.6.0 and is supported until PL 13.2.0. However, it is marked as deprecated, so the compiler may emit deprecation warnings. Ensure that the component is still imported from the library and that no removal occurs in the upcoming PL version."
